                            <comment id="12910646" author="thejas" created="Fri, 17 Sep 2010 17:09:48 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;Example to demonstrate the problem -&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
grunt&amp;gt; run /Users/tejas/pig_unions_udf/trunk/uudf.pig
grunt&amp;gt; l1 = load &apos;/tmp/bag.txt&apos; as (a, b : bag { t : tuple (i : &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;) } );   
grunt&amp;gt; f1 = foreach l1 generate a, MAX(b.i) as mx;  
grunt&amp;gt; describe f1;
f1: {a: bytearray,mx: &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt;}

grunt&amp;gt; l2 = load &apos;/tmp/bag.txt&apos; as (a, b : bag { t : tuple (i : &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;float&lt;/span&gt;) } );
grunt&amp;gt; f2 = foreach l2 generate a, COUNT(b.i) as mx;
grunt&amp;gt; describe f2;
f2: {a: bytearray,mx: &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;long&lt;/span&gt;}

grunt&amp;gt; u = union onschema f1, f2;
grunt&amp;gt; describe u;
u: {a: bytearray,mx: &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;double&lt;/span&gt;}
-- it should be u: {a: bytearray,mx: &lt;span class=&quot;code-object&quot;&gt;long&lt;/span&gt;}
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12912444" author="thejas" created="Mon, 20 Sep 2010 12:55:01 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-1616&quot; title=&quot;&amp;#39;union onschema&amp;#39; does not use create output with correct schema when udfs are involved&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-1616&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-1616&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.1.patch - calls LogicalPlanValidationExecutor.validate() to set the actual types, before the merged schema for &apos;union onschema&apos; is created.&lt;br/&gt;
Passes unit tests and test-patch. Ready for review.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
